# Licensing & How Iris Can Be Used

Hi 👋

Iris is an open-source AI assistant built on **[The Burgess Principle](https://github.com/ljbudgie/burgess-principle)** (UK Certification Mark UK00004343685), created by Lewis James Burgess. This licence reflects the same principles used in the Burgess Principle repository.

